Class MediaArtist

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem2.Artist
      • problem2.MediaArtist
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Actor, Dancer, Filmmaker

    public class MediaArtist
extends Artist
    This class represents a media artist, which include actor, dancer, and filmmaker, with additional given details--lists of movies, series, and other multimedia work the artist was involved with.
